- Okay.

191
00:06:11,139 --> 00:06:13,938
Gye In likes to fish.

192
00:06:13,939 --> 00:06:15,678
- That's right.
- He likes to fish.

193
00:06:15,679 --> 00:06:18,048
After fishing, he would come to my house...

194
00:06:18,049 --> 00:06:20,649
