- Oh, my.

202
00:06:33,559 --> 00:06:36,328
- Did you make him spicy fish stew?
- Yes, I did.

203
00:06:36,329 --> 00:06:37,728
My mom makes really good spicy fish stew.

204
00:06:37,729 --> 00:06:39,768
She told me not to swear at him.

205
00:06:39,769 --> 00:06:41,698
- Her mother cooked for him.
- He's gotten a taste of it,

206
00:06:41,699 --> 00:06:43,509
