238
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,938
- So many men liked her...
- "Sa Mi Ja, sa-gwi-ja."

239
00:07:49,939 --> 00:07:51,838
- and asked her out.
- Exactly.

240
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:54,108
- Her name should be Sa Gwi Ja.
- Right.

241
00:07:54,109 --> 00:07:55,949
- She's so charming.
- Indeed.

242
00:07:56,179 --> 00:07:58,679
