I said that because I wanted to go home.

1239
00:43:02,879 --> 00:43:04,689
Goodness. You missed your husband.

1240
00:43:04,849 --> 00:43:07,049
So in some way, I'm pretty clueless.

1241
00:43:07,349 --> 00:43:08,618
I wasn't that smart about how I lived my life.

1242
00:43:08,619 --> 00:43:09,619
Isn't that right?

1243
00:43:09,620 --> 00:43:11,158
Don't ask me if that's right.

1244
00:43:11,159 --> 00:43:12,929
