- They would go to them.

1256
00:43:35,779 --> 00:43:36,879
- That's right.
- In those days.

1257
00:43:37,079 --> 00:43:39,218
People would ask me for 10,000 or 20,000 dollars.

1258
00:43:39,219 --> 00:43:40,618
- Like that...
- People who ask for money.

1259
00:43:40,619 --> 00:43:43,989
You'd just lend it to them thinking you'd get the interest.

1260
00:43:44,189 --> 00:43:46,758
I observed how Jang Hoon...

1261
00:43:46,759 --> 00:43:48,659
