01:25:02,529 --> 01:25:03,699
Please reveal it.

2439
01:25:03,969 --> 01:25:06,739
Okay. My lie is...

2440
01:25:07,309 --> 01:25:09,809
(Mi Ja didn't play the mom because she was beautiful.)

2441
01:25:10,109 --> 01:25:12,579
(How about me, the woman who played Lee Soon Jae and Shin Gu's mom?)

2442
01:25:12,939 --> 01:25:14,549
My lie is...

2443
01:25:15,679 --> 01:25:17,179
My lie is...

2444
01:25:18,279 --> 01:25:20,018
not attending middle school...

2445
01:25:20,019 --> 01:25:21,748
after failing to pay the entrance fee.

2446
01:25:21,749 --> 01:25:22,948
(Yeong Cheol, Jang Hoon, Kyung Hoon, Shin Young, Young Ok, and Ho Dong)

2447
01:25:22,949 --> 01:25:24,888
- I knew it.
- That's right.

2448
01:25:24,889 --> 01:25:25,958
You just need to go with her choices.

2449
01:25:25,959 --> 01:25:26,959
- That's right.
- Seriously.

2450
01:25:26,960 --> 01:25:28,628
- Did you attend middle school?
- She knows everything.

2451
01:25:28,629 --> 01:25:29,759
- Did you enroll that year?
- Seriously.

2452
01:25:30,029 --> 01:25:32,959
My mom said,

2453
01:25:33,599 --> 01:25:36,999
"We'll harvest rice in autumn,"

2454
01:25:37,099 --> 01:25:39,868
"sell it, and pay for the entrance fee."

2455
01:25:39,869 --> 01:25:42,469
- That much was correct.
- She made that offer.

2456
01:25:42,939 --> 01:25:46,379
But they never told me to pay for the entrance fee.

2457
01:25:46,809 --> 01:25:48,149
Do you know why?

2458
01:25:48,409 --> 01:25:49,979
My homeroom teacher said,

2459
01:25:50,119 --> 01:25:53,419
"If you get an average score of 85 points,"

2460
01:25:53,549 --> 01:25:55,819
"I'll recommend you to become a scholarship student."

2461
01:25:56,349 --> 01:25:58,759
So I studied with all my might.

2462
01:25:58,989 --> 01:26:01,089
I got 100 points for English,

2463
01:26:01,689 --> 01:26:03,189
ninety points for Korean literature,

2464
01:26:03,389 --> 01:26:06,128
and 90 points for history.

2465
01:26:06,129 --> 01:26:07,998
- You scored higher than 85 points.
- That's right.

2466
01:26:07,999 --> 01:26:12,339
"For three years, you can be a scholarship student."

2467
01:26:12,769 --> 01:26:14,008
- I see.
- How cool.

2468
01:26:14,009 --> 01:26:15,909
To this day,

2469
01:26:16,239 --> 01:26:19,138
seeing that school fills my heart...

2470
01:26:19,139 --> 01:26:20,978
with gratitude.

2471
01:26:20,979 --> 01:26:23,048
Were you the first female model for Coca-Cola...

2472
01:26:23,049 --> 01:26:25,178
- in Korea?
- I think I've watched it.

2473
01:26:25,179 --> 01:26:26,448
I think I've watched...

2474
01:26:26,449 --> 01:26:27,648
- the commercial.
- Is it true?

2475
01:26:27,649 --> 01:26:28,888
- Look.
- There is a video.

2476
01:26:28,889 --> 01:26:30,018
- My goodness.
- It's true.

2477
01:26:30,019 --> 01:26:31,019
That's right.

2478
01:26:31,089 --> 01:26:32,188
- Look.
- There is a video.

2479
01:26:32,189 --> 01:26:33,418
- My goodness.
- It's true.

2480
01:26:33,419 --> 01:26:34,428
That's right.

2481
01:26:34,429 --> 01:26:36,329
(The commercial that aired on TV)

2482
01:26:36,429 --> 01:26:40,059
I always buy a 1L Coca-Cola for my family.

2483
01:26:40,369 --> 01:26:42,268
One bottle yields six glasses,

2484
01:26:42,269 --> 01:26:45,238
so it's 12 cents cheaper than the regular bottle.

2485
01:26:45,239 --> 01:26:48,109
- I'm thankful for the company.
- How nice.

2486
01:26:48,909 --> 01:26:50,109
To this day,

2487
01:26:50,839 --> 01:26:53,109
they send me Coca-Cola for Chuseok...

2488
01:26:53,749 --> 01:26:54,808
and Lunar New Year.

2489
01:26:54,809 --> 01:26:56,448
- My goodness.
- That's right. They do that.

2490
01:26:56,449 --> 01:26:57,878
- How cool.
- So...

2491
01:26:57,879 --> 01:26:59,048
It was so much fun.

2492
01:26:59,049 --> 01:27:00,188
(Thanks for the fun story.)

2493
01:27:00,189 --> 01:27:01,688
It was nice to do this together.

2494
01:27:01,689 --> 01:27:04,818
Jang Hoon and Ho Dong did a good job of detecting the lies,

2495
01:27:04,819 --> 01:27:06,488
so they'll get the sweet and refreshing fruits...

2496
01:27:06,489 --> 01:27:08,088
that are full of vitamins,

2497
01:27:08,089 --> 01:27:09,958
- red kiwis.
- That's incredible.

2498
01:27:09,959 --> 01:27:11,258
Red kiwis.

2499
01:27:11,259 --> 01:27:13,568
- Red kiwis.
- Red kiwis.

2500
01:27:13,569 --> 01:27:16,969
The transfer students will also get a present for giving good questions.

2501
01:27:17,469 --> 01:27:19,899
- I can't believe it.
- Congratulations.

2502
01:27:20,509 --> 01:27:23,639
- Red kiwis.
- How was it to be on the show?

2503
01:27:24,509 --> 01:27:28,249
On this popular and nice show,

2504
01:27:28,449 --> 01:27:31,519
I was able to entertain everyone.

2505
01:27:31,849 --> 01:27:33,789
I'm proud of myself.

2506
01:27:34,389 --> 01:27:36,549
(We're proud of being on the show with you.)

2507
01:27:36,819 --> 01:27:39,558
I've wanted to visit this show...

2508
01:27:39,559 --> 01:27:40,828
- for a long time.
- That's right.

2509
01:27:40,829 --> 01:27:44,458
I'm so happy that my dream came true today.

2510
01:27:44,459 --> 01:27:46,968
- Thank you.
- Please visit the show again.

2511
01:27:46,969 --> 01:27:48,198
You know,

2512
01:27:48,199 --> 01:27:49,928
- I laughed when I got invited...
- I think I did well.

2513
01:27:49,929 --> 01:27:51,268
- to Men on a Mission.
- Why?

2514
01:27:51,269 --> 01:27:53,069
I said, "What would we do on that show?"

2515
01:27:53,399 --> 01:27:56,269
But after coming here and hanging out with you guys,

2516
01:27:56,539 --> 01:27:58,379
I feel ten years younger.

2517
01:27:59,179 --> 01:28:01,648
- All right.
- Class really is forever.

2518
01:28:01,649 --> 01:28:03,978
Please be active for the rest of your life.

2519
01:28:03,979 --> 01:28:06,319
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

2520
01:28:07,449 --> 01:28:11,459
(10 years ago, I.O.I graduated after a short period of time.)

2521
01:28:12,459 --> 01:28:15,628
(Let's make a lot of money in the next 10 years...)

2522
01:28:15,629 --> 01:28:17,559
(so that we can reunite and have a concert.)

2523
01:28:17,829 --> 01:28:19,629
(Since then, 10 years have passed.)

2524
01:28:20,059 --> 01:28:22,299
(The familiar faces open the door of the Brother School.)

2525
01:28:22,499 --> 01:28:24,169
(I.O.I reenroll after 10 years.)

2526
01:28:24,439 --> 01:28:27,639
(I.O.I, congratulations on reenrollment)

2527
01:28:27,909 --> 01:28:29,539
(Which member led the reunion?)

2528
01:28:29,769 --> 01:28:32,139
(The great Chungha)

2529
01:28:32,309 --> 01:28:34,479
(Gratitude makes her teary-eyed.)

2530
01:28:34,709 --> 01:28:36,178
(Hey, you have a problem.)

2531
01:28:36,179 --> 01:28:37,479
(Go to a hospital.)

2532
01:28:37,579 --> 01:28:39,119
(The loving advice from a friend of the same age)

2533
01:28:39,519 --> 01:28:42,149
(They become a thorn)

2534
01:28:42,349 --> 01:28:43,418
(Her refreshing charm has leveled up in the past 10 years.)

2535
01:28:43,419 --> 01:28:44,489
(You're good.)

2536
01:28:44,719 --> 01:28:46,289
(May I contact you through your agency?)

2537
01:28:46,389 --> 01:28:48,189
(Her eagerness has leveled up too.)

2538
01:28:48,389 --> 01:28:50,299
(The president of the dance is back.)

2539
01:28:50,629 --> 01:28:52,199
(Make me sweat)

2540
01:28:52,299 --> 01:28:54,769
(Her joints have improved in the past 10 years.)

2541
01:28:54,869 --> 01:28:56,399
(You should do that when you practice.)

2542
01:28:56,899 --> 01:29:00,709
(Do Yeon is back as an actress.)

2543
01:29:01,209 --> 01:29:03,269
(The Blue Dragon Awards winner's pick is Jang Hoon!)

2544
01:29:03,439 --> 01:29:04,538
Jang Hoon is preparing...

2545
01:29:04,539 --> 01:29:06,179
(Jang Hoon is preparing for a wallpapering show.)

2546
01:29:06,279 --> 01:29:07,779
(She is eager for variety shows.)

2547
01:29:07,879 --> 01:29:09,548
(For 3 days,)

2548
01:29:09,549 --> 01:29:11,279
(we'll give a concert.)

2549
01:29:11,379 --> 01:29:12,519
(This is the only chance for you to watch it!)

2550
01:29:12,579 --> 01:29:14,219
(Na Young, you're more glib that I thought.)

2551
01:29:14,389 --> 01:29:16,119
(Stone Na Young has become more glib in the past 10 years.)

2552
01:29:16,419 --> 01:29:19,759
(The youngest one does impressions of the older members.)

2553
01:29:19,919 --> 01:29:21,389
(You haven't changed at all.)

2554
01:29:21,529 --> 01:29:23,129
(So Mi, what are you doing?)

2555
01:29:23,189 --> 01:29:24,599
(Comedians are strict.)

2556
01:29:24,659 --> 01:29:25,659
(Expectant)

2557
01:29:25,899 --> 01:29:26,969
(It's "Pick Me!")

2558
01:29:27,129 --> 01:29:28,829
(They've waited 10 years for this song.)

2559
01:29:31,739 --> 01:29:35,169
(The perfect group dance makes them forget about the past time.)

2560
01:29:35,369 --> 01:29:37,009
- What's going on?
- What?

2561
01:29:37,439 --> 01:29:39,009
(What's the meaning behind So Mi's sudden tears?)

2562
01:29:39,139 --> 01:29:41,709
(Men on a Mission)
